  <summary>3/17/2015--Introduced.
Fairness for Farmers Act of 2015

Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude nonimmigrant agricultural seasonal workers from the definition of "full-time employee" for purposes of the employer mandate to provide employees with minimum essential health care coverage.</summary>
